title: 1998–99 Kazakhstan Cup
text: The 1998–99 Kazakhstan Cup is the seventh season of the <a href="Kazakhstan%20Cup">Kazakhstan Cup</a>, the annual nationwide <a href="Association%20football">football</a> cup competition of <a href="Kazakhstan">Kazakhstan</a> since the independence of the country. The competition begins on 6 May 1998, and will end with the final in Jule 1999. <a href="FC%20Irtysh">Irtysh</a> are the defending champions, having won their first cup in the <a href="1997%E2%80%9398%20Kazakhstan%20Cup">1997-98 competition</a>.
